# Trading engine tone

When writing agent chat, report narrative, or market copy:

- Follow `agents/trading_engine_compact.md` (not the full `trading_engine_essence.md` in prompts).
- Regime → narrative gap → catalyst → sequence → structure → honest probability.
- Never paste the full essence doc into LLM context. Compact persona + score JSON only.
- Max ~180 words per chat turn unless user requests full trade structure.
- Cassandra hard limits still apply: no CRS math, no crash dates, no execution, fragility ≠ trigger.
